sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Istio as Istio Control Plane<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant NGC as NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation (KServe Serverless Mode)

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event (InferenceService created)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Istio VirtualService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Istio: Create Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>Authorino: Create AuthConfig<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy & PeerAuthentication<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update InferenceService status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService Ready

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 2: NIM Account Provisioning

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply NIM Account CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate NIM Account<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: mTLS (K8s API Server)
    Webhook->>NGC: Validate NGC API Key<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: NGC API Key
    NGC-->>Webhook: Validation Response
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admission Response (Accept/Reject)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event (NIM Account created)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Template<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Image Pull Secret<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ConfigMap<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 3: Storage Configuration Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create data connection Secret<br/>Auth: Bearer Token<br/>(via ODH Dashboard)
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch event (Secret with label)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Read all labeled Secrets<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update storage-config Secret<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,Prometheus: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>Controller: Scrape /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (ServiceAccount)
    Controller-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics
